CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FThe Ayatollah was killed in the first
OL,7,Fwave of US and Israeli strikes on
OL,8,FTehran on Saturday morning.
OL,10,FMs Zaghari-Ratcliffe said there was
OL,11,Flots of "fear and uncertainty about
OL,12,Fwhat happens next" after the death of
OL,13,FKhamenei, mixed ` for many Iranians `
OL,14,Fwith "happiness and relief".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
