OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FKhamenei, who succeeded the Islamic
OL,7,FRepublic's founding leader, Ayatollah
OL,8,FRuhollah Khomeini, as Supreme Leader
OL,9,Fin 1989, was a ruthless revolutionary.
OL,10,FDuring his three decades as leader,
OL,11,Fthe 86-year-old built the paramilitary
OL,12,FRevolutionary Guard into a powerful
OL,13,Fforce that underpinned his rule.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
