PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FThe latest protests in January, which
OL,7,Fbegan over the deteriorating economic
OL,8,Fsituation and escalated to become a
OL,9,Fwider outcry against the theocratic
OL,10,Fgovernment, were suppressed with force.
OL,12,FMore than 36,500 Iranians were killed
OL,13,Fby security forces during the
OL,14,Fcrackdown on nationwide protests,
OL,15,Fmaking it the deadliest two-day
OL,16,Fprotest massacre in history, according
OL,17,Fto documents reviewed by Iran
OL,18,FInternational's Editorial Board.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,F"Ideally, it should have been a fair
OL,7,Ftrial," Ms Zaghari-Ratcliffe said of
OL,8,FKhamenei's death. "He should have
OL,9,Fstood a trial in a public court in
OL,10,Ffront of the people whom he had
OL,11,Fcommitted crimes against".
OL,13,F"It was a very easy exit for him,
OL,14,Ffrankly. But I also understand, you
OL,15,Fknow, for those people who were
OL,16,Fcheering in the streets, both inside
OL,17,FIran and outside, that there was a
OL,18,Fmoment of happiness, but I think there
OL,19,Fwas a lot of also fear and uncertainty
OL,20,Fthat comes with it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FMs Zaghari-Ratcliffe said: "If there
OL,7,Fis going to be any transition, it's
OL,8,Fgoing to be long and it's going to be,
OL,9,Fin my opinion, not much different to
OL,10,Fwhat it used to be.
OL,12,F"That makes me so worried about what
OL,13,Fis going to happen next," she said.
OL,14,F"The political structure will not
OL,15,Fautomatically become democratic."
OL,17,FBut, she said, there was "quiet hope"
OL,18,Fthat with the death of Khamenei, there
OL,19,Fwas a path to change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,F"I think at the moment there is
OL,7,Fprobably a quiet hope...They
OL,8,F(Iranians) are fearful of what's going
OL,9,Fto happen next but it's definitely the
OL,10,Fbeginning of the end. It's not going
OL,11,Fto happen instantly and overnight."
OL,13,FMs Zaghari-Ratcliffe reacts to the
OL,14,Fdeath of Khamenei: "This is not how he
OL,15,Fshould have gone"
OL,26,@pD@ApmpD@Jpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FShe said she had been "unsettled" ever
OL,7,Fsince hearing the news of US-Israel
OL,8,Fstrikes on Saturday, adding: "I put
OL,9,Fsome podcast on and I went and sat at
OL,10,Fmy sewing machine. That's what makes
OL,11,Fme really calm down and focus."
OL,13,FAfter hearing about Khamenei's
OL,14,Freported death from a friend, Ms
OL,15,FZaghari-Ratcliffe described feeling
OL,16,F"in shock" and disbelieving of whether
OL,17,For not it was confirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,F"What if we wake up in the morning
OL,7,F(and) that wasn't the truth. So just
OL,8,Fbeing a bit cautious on how we reflect
OL,9,Fon such news," she said.
OL,11,FShe insisted that the "UK government
OL,12,Fmust stand with the people of Iran"
OL,13,Fand that policy "cannot be this
OL,14,Fincoherent".
OL,16,F"There was a moment of happiness and
OL,17,Frelief... but also there is a lot of
OL,18,Ffear and uncertainty that what comes
OL,19,Fafter that"
OL,26,@oD@ApmoD@Epn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
