OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FMs Zaghari-Ratcliffe, a British-
OL,7,FIranian dual citizen, was arrested in
OL,8,F2016 on charges of plotting to
OL,9,Foverthrow the government during a
OL,10,Fvisit to her parents with her 22-month-
OL,11,Fold daughter Gabriella.
OL,13,FHer husband, Richard, fought
OL,14,Ftirelessly to bring his wife back to
OL,15,FBritain after years of campaigning. Ms
OL,16,FZaghari-Ratcliffe was finally freed in
OL,17,FMarch 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News alongside his
OL,7,Fwife, Mr Zaghari-Ratcliffe said: "I
OL,8,Ffelt the UK policy on Iran could be
OL,9,Fquite contradictory over the years
OL,10,Fthat we were campaigning.
OL,12,F"It still feels quite contradictory.
OL,13,FIt still feels that it's not focused
OL,14,Fon keeping people safe, such as Brits
OL,15,Fbeing held imprisoned in Iran, and
OL,16,FBritish-Iranians who are there. "
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,FHe referenced the plight of Lindsay
OL,7,Fand Craig Foreman, a British couple
OL,8,Ffrom Sussex currently being held in an
OL,9,FIranian prison, saying the British
OL,10,Fgovernment's response has been "kind
OL,11,Fof victim-blaming".
OL,13,FThey were arrested while travelling
OL,14,Fthrough Iran in January 2025 and later
OL,15,Fsentenced to 10 years in prison for
OL,16,Fespionage ` charges they deny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,F"One of the promises that the
OL,7,Fgovernment made after Nazanin's case
OL,8,Fwas that they were going to have an
OL,9,Fimproved approach to dealing with
OL,10,Fhostages... They haven't kept those
OL,11,Fpromises," he added.
OL,13,F"So every time I've ever seen a news
OL,14,Freport, the briefing that the
OL,15,Fgovernment has put out has been that
OL,16,Fthe problem was that they ignored
OL,17,Ftravel advice and that they shouldn't
OL,18,Fhave gone there...No one deserves to
OL,19,Fbe a hostage."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,F"I find it really traumatising that I
OL,7,Fcannot contact my family"
OL,9,FFollowing Saturday's strikes on Tehran
OL,10,Fand other major cities in Iran, the
OL,11,Fconflict has escalated and threatens
OL,12,Fto drag the wider Middle Eastern
OL,13,Fregion into war.
OL,15,FMs Zaghari-Ratcliffe said the
OL,16,Fsituation in Iran was "very worrying"
OL,17,Fand that it was "traumatising" not to
OL,18,Fbe able to contact her elderly parents
OL,19,Fthere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1772539377
OL,3,CNazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe says there
OL,4,Cis 'quiet hope' for Iranian people
OL,6,F"I try not to check the news, but it
OL,7,Fis impossible not to think, are they
OL,8,Fsafe? It's just such worrying times.
OL,9,FIt has been very, very difficult to
OL,10,Fget hold of them."
OL,12,FShe said this could be a pivotal
OL,13,Fmoment for Iran's future, adding: "I
OL,14,Fthink we are close. Maybe not that
OL,15,Fclose, but definitely closer".
OL,17,F"There is hope and Iranians, just like
OL,18,Fso many other nations, deserve to live
OL,19,Ffree and to be happy."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
